T02TD2323E:265a-1: tsitta gu hya pra d'i pam n'a ma /
T02TD2323E:265a-3: gsang ba thugs kyi sgron ma zhes bya ba /
T02TD2323E:265a-4: 'jam dpal smra ba'i seng ge la phyag 'tshal lo //
T02TD2323E:265a-5: dam pa lnga bcu rtsa lnga yis //
T02TD2323E:265a-6: zhabs kyi padmar rab btud nas //
T02TD2323E:265a-7: sdug bsngal zhi bar bya ba'i phyir //
T02TD2323E:265a-8: khyad par lnga yis gdams pa bstan //
T02TD2323E:265a-9: kye ma rnam shes rlung gis 'khrugs //
T02TD2323E:265a-10: rlung ni las su rung ba dang //
T02TD2323E:265a-11: gtum mo rlung gis sbar bar bya //
T02TD2323E:265a-12: 'du ba'i nad kyang rlung gis bcos //
T02TD2323E:265a-13: 'byung ba ro ni mnyam pa dang //
T02TD2323E:265a-14: brtul zhugs spyod pas bar chod sel //
T02TD2323E:265a-15: 'tsho ba'i bcud ni len pa dang //
T02TD2323E:265a-16: ae wam bde ba'i rlung gis bskyed //
T02TD2323E:265a-18: rdo rje rkang mgyogs grub par 'gyur //
T02TD2323E:265a-19: dh'u t'ir tshud de phyag rgya che //
T02TD2323E:265a-21: rtsa dang rlung dang byang chub sems //
T02TD2323E:265a-22: stong phrag bdun cu rtsa gnyis ni //
T02TD2323E:265a-23: chags dang 'bri ba bcu gnyis brgya //
T02TD2323E:265a-24: la la ra sa dh'u t'ar bsdu //
T02TD2323E:265a-25: rlung dang byang chub sems kyang de //
T02TD2323E:265a-26: 'khor lo bzhi la srog shing tshul //
T02TD2323E:265a-28: bcu drug phyed phyed thig le ni //
T02TD2323E:265b-0: dkyil dang bzlog dang dgram zhing @265b bstim //
T02TD2323E:265b-1: dga' bzhi'i khyad par phyag rgya che //
T02TD2323E:265b-3: shes pa kho na 'ba' zhig yin //
T02TD2323E:265b-4: sems ni kun gyi sa bon te //
T02TD2323E:265b-5: rang sems rtogs nas sangs rgyas la //
T02TD2323E:265b-6: bde ba gzhan du mi btsal lo //
T02TD2323E:265b-7: sems nyid las su rung ba dang //
T02TD2323E:265b-8: rnam par mi rtog yang dag don //
T02TD2323E:265b-9: gnyis med gnyis su med pa las //
T02TD2323E:265b-10: gnyis su byar med spros bral mkha' //
T02TD2323E:265b-11: srid dang mya ngan 'das las grol //
T02TD2323E:265b-12: don gyis dbu ma phyag rgya che //
T02TD2323E:265b-13: snying po'i don la sa ma yengs par //
T02TD2323E:265b-14: gnyug ma'i yid ni gcig tu gtad //
T02TD2323E:265b-15: rnal ma'i don la rab gnas nas /
T02TD2323E:265b-16: yid la mi dmigs bde ba che //
T02TD2323E:265b-17: lhan cig skyes pa bdud rtsi'i ro //
T02TD2323E:265b-18: mtshon du yod pa ma yin te //
T02TD2323E:265b-19: ston ka'i zla ltar dri med 'od //
T02TD2323E:265b-20: bde gsal stong pa'i ye shes can //
T02TD2323E:265b-21: rang la spras pa mig ltar dbye //
T02TD2323E:265b-22: bde ba che las gzhan med pas //
T02TD2323E:265b-23: phyag rgya'i mchog de phyag rgya che //
T02TD2323E:265b-24: sdug bsngal zhi bar bya ba dang //
T02TD2323E:265b-25: lus sems 'phyan du gzhug pa dang //
T02TD2323E:265b-26: 'bras bu blo yis ma grub pa //
T02TD2323E:265b-27: shes rgyud nam mkhar 'phang ba dang //
T02TD2323E:265b-28: dmigs pa sna tshogs bsgyur shes so //
T02TD2323E:265b-29: chos dang chos min sel ba dang //
T02TD2323E:265b-30: rig pa dangs snyigs dbye ba dang //
T02TD2323E:265b-31: rnam shes rlung yang bstim pa'o //
T02TD2323E:265b-32: sgyu lus 'od gsal bsre bar bya //
T02TD2323E:265b-33: bag chags sbubs su grol ba dang //
T02TD2323E:265b-34: phyag rgya chen po dus 'dir thob //
T02TD2323E:265b-35: des na rnal 'byor brtson par bya //
T02TD2323E:265b-36: sdug bsngal zhi bar byed pa gsang ba thugs kyi sgron ma zhes bya ba //
T02TD2323E:265b-37: rnal 'byor gyi dbang phyug chen bo ka ma la sh'i las mdzad pa rdzogs so /
T02TD2323E:265b-39: // / rgya gar gyi mkhan po dzny'a na gu hya dang /
T02TD2323E:265b-40: bod kyi lo ts'a ba lo btsun chung gis brgyur ba'o//
